  <description>
    <p>Multi-client for the Bitwarden速 platform and KeePass (KDBX), created to provide the best user experience possible.</p>
    <p>Can be used with any Bitwarden速 installation. This product is not associated with the Bitwarden project nor Bitwarden, Inc. Bitwarden速 is a registered trademark of Bitwarden Inc.</p>
    <p>Highlights</p>
    <ul>
      <li>a beautiful rich and responsive <em>Material You</em> user interface;</li>
      <li>a <em>powerful</em> and <em>fast search</em>;</li>
      <li>a watchtower that finds items with <em>Pwned passwords</em>, <em>Vulnerable accounts</em>, <em>Reused passwords</em>, <em>Inactive two factor authentication</em>, <em>Inactive passkeys</em>, <em>Unsecure Websites</em> as well as <em>Duplicate</em>, <em>Incomplete</em> and <em>Expiring</em> items, and other;</li>
      <li><em>multi-account support</em> with secure login and two-factor authentication support;</li>
      <li>add items and sends (Bitwarden), modify, and view your vault <em>offline</em>;</li>
      <li><em>export individual</em> or organization items, <em>including the attachments</em>;</li>
      <li>beautiful <em>Light</em>/<em>Dark theme</em>;</li>
      <li>a generator with <em>SSH keys</em>, <em>Email forwarders</em>, <em>Custom wordlists</em> support, and many other features; </li>
      <li>a support for <em>shortcuts</em>, <em>placeholders</em> and <em>URL overrides</em>;</li>
      <li>a <em>smart conflict resolution</em>;</li>
      <li>and much more!</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
